Resulting Actions: The GUI screen displays the home page. The success message 1 is displayed on top of the screen.

Trigger: User clicks the Previous Page (Left Arrow) Button.
Resulting Actions: The GUI screen displays the previous page if the user is not on the home page. The success message 2 is displayed on top of the screen.

Trigger: User clicks the Next Page (Right Arrow) Button.
Resulting Actions: The GUI screen displays the next page if the user is on the home page or any page after. The success message 3 is displayed on top of the screen.
